      (c.id, 'ADA1-E05005-INS', 'Adande', 'Del-Install', 'To attend site during normal working hours weekdays to carry out the following work in one continuous operation: A) Strip out and remove for safe disposal 1No. Existing Adande unit. B) Deliver, position, install and commission equipment as quoted above. All work is to be carried out in one continuous operation in one site visit. See Delivery Notes below.', 300.00, 0.00, '0825-067', 'Aug 2025'),
