      (c.id, 'AMB1-E0001', 'Ambach', 'EF245EE', 'Electric deep fat fryer with (2) pans, (2) baskets, safety cut-out, thermostatic control, 12-13L Oil Capacity, 90°C to 195°C temp range, (2) heating elements Power: 400V (3N~) / 50Hz / 32A Dimensions: 450mm(w) x 920mm(d) x 750mm(h) Prices includes side panel and infill element Warranty: 1 Year Parts and Labour', 6187.93, 0.00, '0226-002', 'Feb 2026'),
