      (c.id, 'AMB1-E00004', 'Ambach', '8GHUBG80H', 'Range with 4 open burners. Heavy duty burners sealed to the moulded pan. Power control via heavy duty gas valves, large double ring main burners, pilot flame protected and integrated in the burner, gas main shut off valve as a standard. Appliance complete with edge free 2mm thick top and sturdy upper frame construction. The modular assembly incorporates a "seamless joining system". The unit is a full high module on base unit with gn 2/1 electric oven with total capacity: 535x660x270, base unit with self-supporting, box-type, construction. Total nominal power: 34,1kW, 3/4" gas, IP protection degree: ipx4, net weight: 155 kg. Dimensions: 800mm(w) x 850mm(d) x 750mm(h) NOTE: Price includes Pilot protection cover per burner and shipping from manufacturer Warranty: 1 Year Parts & Labour', 5735.52, 0.00, '0226-032', 'Feb 2026'),
      (c.id, 'AMB1-E00010', 'Ambach', 'S8ETEUBS60EC', 'S8ETEUBS60EC, Electric Deep Fat Fryer', 7872.77, 0.00, '0426-037', 'Apr 2026'),
