      (c.id, 'AMB1-E00030', 'Ambach', 'Cooksuite', 'To supply only 1no. bespoke Ambach Cooksuite section approx. 1800mm wide x 850mm deep x 750mm high to be fitted onto existing plinth. Cooksuite to comprise of the following (from left to right as viewed from operator) - 2no. 600mm wide electric deep fat fryers with single pan to each unit. Each well to have Tempura drip racks. Under to be ambient base unit with oil container and hinged door. - 1no. 150mm wide neutral infill element with closed façade to front - 1no. 500mm wide electric deep fat fryer with double pan. Under to be ambient base unit with oil container and hinged door. - 1No. 25ml 3 metre round power pole. Unit to have one piece top with rounded corners and control panel applied. Warranty: 1 Year Parts & Labour', 0.00, 0.00, '0426-037', 'Apr 2026'),
      (c.id, 'AMB1-E0006-AC', 'Ambach', 'WD', 'Wing Door', 232.76, 0.00, '0426-037', 'Apr 2026'),
      (c.id, 'FLA1-V0001', 'Ansul', 'Ansul Fire Suppression System', 'To supply, install, test and comission the following Ansul R102 Fire Suppresion systems to the following cooking stations only: Hot Kitchen to have 1no. four tank system covering 6no. canopy spigots, 4no induction hobs, 1no. fryer, 1no. griddle, 1no. Charcoal Grill, 1no. Charcoal oven and 1no. salamander grill Pastry kitchen to have 1no. Single tank system to cover 2no. canopy spigots Prep Kitchen to have 1no. Single Tank System to cover 1no. canopy spigot and 1no. induction hob The system shall be an Ansul R102 fire suppression system which is mechanically operated, utilising automatic fusible link detectors, positioned within the cooker hood, plenum area. A manual release point shall also be provided adjacent to the kitchen exit. The system will be provided with an interface panel which ', 15784.00, 0.00, '1025-010', 'Oct 2025'),
      (c.id, 'JES1-E0042', 'Antunes', 'VCT-2000', 'Double-Sided Vertical Contact Toaster. Features a digital controller for making precise adjustments to the quality of the toast for different bread products. A built-in auxiliary heater warms the top sides of the buns to help keep the assembled sandwich warmer for longer. Also includes belt wraps to minimize bun marking. Available features for the unit include a wide mouth bun feeder, motorized butter wheel, heated base, and back plate. Dimensions: 540mm(w) x 387mm(d) x 591mm(h) Warranty: 1 Years Parts & Labour', 7374.00, 50.00, '0525-054', 'May 2025'),
      (c.id, 'JES1-E0041', 'Antunes', 'VCT-1000', 'The VCT-1000 model features a dial thermostat for adjusting the quality of the toast for a variety of different bread products. Available preset toast times range from 10 seconds to 28 seconds Dimensions: 540mm(w) x 387mm(d) x 616mm(h) Warranty: 1 Years Parts & Labour', 2599.00, 0.00, '0525-054', 'May 2025'),
      (c.id, 'ANV1-00001', 'Anvil', 'Site Work - Anvil', 'To attend site during normal working hours to carry out the following in one continous operation: A) Remove existing ceiling grid. B) Supply and install new section of suspended ceiling and tiles to match the existing. C) Remove and replace the safety bar outside for access to the compressor. D) Isolate and cap off existing power to the cold room. E) Supply and fit a 230/1/50 16A motor rated electrical supply to the control panel location. F) Supply and fit a 400/3/50 20A supply at the remote condensing unit, including external isolator. G) Relocate existing light fittings. H) Remove the sink, drain dosing system and clear the space for the new coldroom. All hot and cold feeds / drainage to be removed and capped off at source.# I) Repair / replace floor tiles on removal of the cold room fr', 7854.00, 0.00, '1125-049', 'Nov 2025'),
      (c.id, 'MID1-E00032', 'APW Wyott', 'M-95-2', 'Bun Grill toaster, Generates up to 865 bun halves per hour, 200°C - 500°C Thermostatically controlled griddle plate, includes (2) PTFE sheets, Adjustable legs, Self-levelling conveyor. Power: 230V 11.1A Dimensions: 556mm(w) x 447mm(d) x 699mm(h) Warranty: 1 Year Parts and Labour', 2828.00, 0.00, '0226-058', 'Feb 2026'),
      (c.id, 'FOG1-E0001', 'Aquarius', 'FOGTRAP', 'Fogtrap Fat Oil and Grease Interceptor Unit *MAINTENANCE CONTRACT TO BE SETUP DIRECT BETWEEN FOGTRAP AND THE CLIENT FOR REMOVAL AND REPLACEMENT ON REGULAR BASIS - THIS IS NOT INCLUDED IN THIS PRICE*', 495.00, 0.00, '0226-079', 'Feb 2026'),
      (c.id, 'ATH1-E0002', 'Athanor', 'Bespoke', 'To manufacture, supply, delivery and installation of proposed Athanor island suite having an overall footprint of 5735mm (long) x 1750mm (wide) x 810mm (high) Unit to be manufactured as per layout and be mounted on existing concrete plinth Unit to comprise of the following; 1x 3mm one-piece chrome titanium stainless steel alloy primary top 1x 100mm high upstand to rear cut-out section being formed as part of the primary top Set flush in to the primary top is to be; A – 3 off – twin zone (4kW + 4kW) 750mm single plate Plaque Athanor cooking plate / plancha B – 1 off – twin zone (5kW + 5kW) multi-point ceran glass induction hob C – 2 off – single zone (4k) 375mm single plate Plaque Athanor cooking plate / plancha D – 2 off – multi-zone (14kW) multi-point ceran glass induction hob E – 2 off –', 159685.00, 0.00, '0125-035', 'Jan 2025'),
      (c.id, 'JES1-E00019', 'Ayrking', 'AYBBS-U-4221-SH', 'AyrKing BBSU4221- portable automatic Blender/Sifter machine, Sift and blend 30 lbs (14 kg) of breading in 60 seconds, Rotary auger brush blends, sifts, and ejects dough balls simultaneously, Blending brush action prevents ingredient segregation, unlike vibrating or, agitating systems, Quiet, vibration-free operation creates results, not disturbances, Sixty second timed cycle frees labor and saves energy, Fully enclosed sifter with only four internal parts, reduces dust and allows quick and easy cleaning , Direct drive, steel geared motor & solid stainless steel fabrication provide lasting performance, Lockable casters and small footprint make this the ultimate portable breading station . Dimensions: 1194mm(l) x 635mm(w) x 1168mm(h) Warranty: 1 Year Parts & Labour', 8172.00, 50.00, '0125-050', 'Jan 2025'),
      (c.id, 'MID1-E0007', 'Bakers Pride', 'P22-BL', 'Two 15-minute, electric timers with continuous-ring alarm and manual shut-off, One baking chamber, Two decks, Independent top and bottom controlled incoloy heating elements, 70mm & 83mm deck heights , Brick-Lined Chambers, All stainless steel exterior, Fully insulated, 102mm adjustable legs Power: 230V 1Ph 16A or 230-400V 3Ph 20A Dimensions: 660mm(w) x 711mm(d) x 432mm(h) (Height excludes feet) Warranty: 1 Years Parts and Labour', 6088.00, 0.00, '0126-029', 'Jan 2026'),
