      (c.id, 'CAM1-R0025', 'Cambro', 'MSU45918PKG', 'Camshelving Starter Unit 4-tier vented includes: (2) posts kits 4 shelf kits rust free polymer coated steel speckled white HACCP Dimensions 1800(h) x 980(w) x 500(d) ** Lifetime guarantee against rust.**', 500.00, 45.00, '0325-040', 'Mar 2025'),
