      (c.id, 'CAR1-E0014', 'Carpigarni', 'LABO 8/12 XPL P', 'The Labo 8/12 XPL P is the perfect solution for those looking for a high-performance counter-top batch freezer. Ideal for food service and catering, making is possible to freeze gelato and sorbets. Features & benefits: • LCD screen consistently displays the values of the programmed consistency and the gelato in the batch freezer. • Pom Beater: No central shaft and has removeable POM blades. • Post Cooling- Cooling function injects cold into the gelato as it comes out of the cylinder. • The delayed cleaning program guarantees hygiene by controlling the temperature of the cylinder once the gelato has been extracted • Versatile shelf, possibility of positioning the shelf at two different heights and in three different positions. Specifications: •Hourly Production: Min- 8KG Max- 12KG •Quantity', 12412.00, 40.00, '1025-010', 'Oct 2025'),
      (c.id, 'CAR1-E00013', 'Carpigiani', 'READY 8 12', 'High performance combination machine, self-pasturising, max 2.5kg/cycle output. Dimensions: 740mm(w) x 360mm(d) x 550mm(h) Warranty: 1 Year Parts and Labour', 8738.40, 0.00, '0126-004', 'Jan 2026'),
