      (c.id, 'HER1-001', 'Eclat De France', 'Claire', 'The CLAIRE Burnisher is specially designed for cleaning, maintenance, and restoration of silver-plated items, stainless steel, and other noble metals such as copper, tin, vermeil, gold, bronze, and brass. This compact, stainless steel machine is mounted on wheels and features a removable tank for easy cleaning and maintenance. Complete with 70Kgs of stainless steel balls. Maximum capacity: 60 pieces of cutlery (e.g., teaspoons) ~ 40 pieces (knives, forks, tablespoons) Cycle time: 5 to 15 minutes for regular maintenance, depending on wear and metal hardness (60-minute timer) Conveyor speed: adjustable from 16 to 40 cm/sec (machine equipped with a motorized speed variator) • Minimum speed (16 cm/sec): for plates and serving trays (maximum dimensions: 36 x 26 cm) • Medium speed (28 cm/sec): f', 13650.00, 0.00, '0725-038', 'Jul 2025'),
