      (c.id, 'FAL1-E0057', 'Falcon Foodservice Equipment', 'G3101', 'Dominator Plus Medium Duty Range gas 900mm (6) hob burners standard oven (2) shelves piezo ignition thermostatic control (2) side hinged doors enamel oven interior stainless steel exterior Gas rating: 146 000 btu/hr (gross) / 38.9kW (Nett) Dimensions: 900mm(w) x 770mm(d) x 890mm(h) Warranty: 1 Year Parts & Labour', 1355.00, 0.00, '0925-095', 'Sep 2025'),
