      (c.id, 'FAL1-E0108', 'Falcon Foodservice Equipment', 'ORXSTG', 'The Lainox Oracle XS is a compact high-speed oven for fast cooking, reheating and regeneration. It uses a combination of convection heat, microwave energy and high-speed impingement air to deliver consistent results in reduced cooking times. Supplied with a 13A plug, the oven can be installed in a wide range of locations without complex electrical requirements. Operation is via a colour touchscreen controller with programmable cooking cycles. The integrated Oracle Odorless System removes cooking odours, supporting installation without a separate ventilation canopy. This version features a stainless steel exterior for durability and ease of cleaning. Dimensions: 356mm (w) x 588mm (d) x 580mm (h) Warranty: 2 Years Parts & Labour', 6335.00, 55.00, '0426-069', 'Apr 2026'),
