      (c.id, 'FAR1-E0021', 'Far East', 'IS8', 'Freestanding Induction stockpot stove Backsplash mounted goose neck swivel water spout with level action control for filling tall pots Intuitive sliding power control Backsplash mounted LED display showing power level, electricity consumption, induction element temperature and diagnostic codes Dry pan and overheat protection prevent induction driver and coil overheating Stainless steel construction Electrical load - 8 kW 3 phase induction (12A or 22A/f 400V) equivalent to 37 kW gas burner Dimensions - 650mm wide x 570mm deep x 550 / 1250mm high (plus 300mm for water spout) Warranty - 12 month parts only warranty Supplied with 70L lidded stock pot (Ø430xH520)', 2300.00, 25.00, '0825-095', 'Aug 2025'),
      (c.id, 'FAR1-E0020', 'Far East', 'IW19', 'Freestanding Induction wok range. Each ring has 8 kW 3 phase induction equivalent power to 40 kW gas turbo burner – boils 1L water in 45 secs (from 15°c to 95°c in a cold wok) Twin Ø300 wok rings front and central flat Ø280 ring for stockpot to rear (2f1r) Backsplash mounted swivel water spout with level action controls Intuitive power slider control suitable for operation with knees (hands free operation) Front mounted drainage channel with removable filter Backsplash mounted LED display showing power level, electricity consumption, induction element temperature and diagnostic codes Air cooled “waterless” technology: save 1000 of litres vs cookers that need a water bath Modular design allows units to be clipped together to provide desired cookline Automatic pan detection deactivates heat ', 8200.00, 25.00, '0925-090', 'Sep 2025'),
