      (c.id, 'FOS1-E5001-INS', 'Foster', 'STRIP OUT', 'To attend site during normal working hours weekdays to a clear and level site free from other trades to degas and remove from site for disposal 3no. existing cold rooms and 3no. modular blast chillers in readiness for the delivery and installation of Item 1.01 and 1.02 above. Site maintenance to be in attendnace to advise on termination and isolation points.All works to be carried out in accordance with Site Work Specification below.', 13267.00, 0.00, '0725-033', 'Jul 2025'),
