      (c.id, 'FOS1-E00027', 'Fosters', 'EMD900G', 'The EMD900G is fitted as standard with enticing LED uplighting (patent pending) with anti-glare feature to brightly illuminate the brands on offer. With an energy grade of B and a 330ml drink capacity of 408 (without double stacking), this Multideck provides fantastic capacity with low running costs.Fitted at no extra cost, its +stayclear condenser reduces the amount of time required for maintenance, saving money by reducing the chance of blockage and potential breakdown. Maximum visibility through large glass side panels means customers no longer have to be directly in front to see stored goods.The clean aesthetic gives centre stage to stored products. Doors are lockable as standard and swivel castors are supplied for easy movement making cleaning in and around the multideck easier than e', 8060.00, 52.50, '0125-015', 'Jan 2025'),
