      (c.id, 'HEN1-E00018', 'Henkelman', 'Jumbo 42', 'Jumbo 42 • Supplied with one sealing bar as standard (front) • Double seal as standard (two sealing wires). Optional at no extra cost: Cut-off/Wide seal • Easy-to-remove sealing bar for easy cleaning • Pump maintenance and cleaning program • Digital time control with single program panel as standard • Stainless steel casing and transparent lid • Supplied with two insert plates for a faster cycle and good product positioning Dimensions (Machine): 490mm(w) x 530mm(d) x 440mm(h) Warranty: 1 Year Parts Only', 1299.00, 0.00, '0325-106', 'Mar 2025'),
      (c.id, 'HEN1-E00017', 'Henkelman', 'Boxer 42', 'The robust, stainless steel Boxer 42 vacuum packaging machine is standard equipped with a Busch vacuum pump and Digital control with a 10 program memory. This table-top model complies with CE standards. Standard with 1 seal bar (front): 420 mm Standard double seal (two wires). Seal bar easily removable for cleaning and maintenance purposes. Pump capacity: 21 m3/h Busch vacuum pump. Pump maintenance and cleaning program. Machine cycle: 15-35 sec. Standard Digital control with Time control and a 10 program memory. Standard Soft Air to protect the product and vacuum bag. Deep drawn stainless steel vacuum chamber. Stainless steel exterior and transparent lid. Comes with insert plate for a faster cycle and product adjustment Dimensions: 528mm(w) x 493mm(d) x 440mm(h) (720mm with lid open) Warra', 1535.00, 0.00, '0125-002', 'Jan 2025'),
      (c.id, 'HEN1-E0007', 'Henkelman BV', 'Boxer 42XL', 'Boxer 42XL • Supplied with one sealing bar as standard (front) • Double seal as standard (two sealing wires). • Easy-to-remove sealing bar for easy cleaning • Pump maintenance and cleaning program • Digital time control with ten-program memory as standard • Soft Air as standard to protect the product and vacuum bag • Stainless steel casing and transparent lid • Supplied with three insert plates for a faster cycle and good product positioning Dimensions (machine): 490mm(w) x 615mm(d) x 440mm(h) Warranty: 1 Year Parts', 1649.00, 0.00, '0325-087', 'Mar 2025'),
      (c.id, 'HEN1-E0001', 'Henkleman', 'Jumbo 42', 'Jumbo Series Vacuum Packaging Machine table model (1) 420 mm removable seal bar with double seal 16m/hr vacuum pump capacity 370mm x 420mm x 180mm chamber multifunction controls stop button air flow return insert plates for fast vacuum cycle and product adjustment transparent lid full stainless steel construction 0.55 kW. Dimensions: 480mm(w) x 525mm(d) x 430mm(h) Warranty: 1 Year Parts & Labour', 1299.00, 0.00, '0125-002', 'Jan 2025'),
      (c.id, 'JES1-E00038', 'Henny Penny', 'HPEEG242', 'Henny Penny HP-EEG242 Evolution Elite Open Fryer, gas, double well, with reduced oil capacity technology, sensor activated Oil Guardian™, automatically replenishes oil, with oil reservoir, iControl™, 230v/50Hz/1-ph, 2.5 amps, 75,000 BTU, 44.2KW Dimensions: 794mm (w) x 819mm (d) x 1162mm (h) Warranty: 2 Years Parts & Labour', 39412.00, 50.00, '1225-032', 'Dec 2025'),
      (c.id, 'JES1-E00025', 'Henny Penny', 'HPGVE071', 'Manual Low Oil Volume Open Fryer, electric, (1) well, 18.3 L capacity per full vat, (40) programmable cook programs, LED display, built-in manual filtration, high-limit temperature protection, (4) swivel castors (2 locking), stainless steel construction, 220/380v/50/3-ph, 14.0 kW, 24.3 amps, CE Dimensions: 434mm(w) x 842mm(d) x 1185mm(h) Warranty: 2 Years Parts & Labour', 14870.00, 50.00, '0125-050', 'Jan 2025'),
      (c.id, 'JES1-E00041', 'Henny Penny', 'HPGVE072', 'Manual Low Oil Volume Open Fryer, electric, (2) wells, 18.3 L capacity per full vat, (40) programmable cook programs, LED display, built-in manual filtration, high-limit temperature protection, (4) swivel castors (2 locking), stainless steel construction, 220/380v/50/3-ph, 28.0 kW, 48.6 amps, CE. Dimensions: 794mm(w) x 842mm(d) x 1185mm(h) Warranty: 2 Years Parts & Labour', 21992.00, 50.00, '0125-050', 'Jan 2025'),
      (c.id, 'HOB1-E00015', 'Hobart', 'H600SN-2351-SS', 'Floor Standing Mixer Model: H600SN-2351-SS, Services: 1.5kW 230/50/1 Capacity: 60 Litres Corrosion Resistant with no paint to chip on potentially vulnerable areas and sturdy stainless steel base frame and pedestal. Standard Features-Large 60 Litre Capacity the Direct Drive Via A Full Gearbox Enables Heavy Loads To Be Mixed With All Speeds Being Consistent. Operation Safety Is Considered Paramount And Our Mixers Are Supplied Complete With A Safety Guard And No Volt Release Switch which Prevents Accidental Restart Of The Machine If The Power Supply Is Interrupted. The Mixer Can Be Fitted With A Variety Of Attachments Along With A Smaller Bowl, Which Gives You Greater Flexibility And Economy. Comes Complete With Timer, Stainless Steel Bowl, Beater, Whip And Hook. The European Standard En454: ', 17821.44, 0.00, '0525-102', 'May 2025'),
      (c.id, 'HOB1-E00392', 'Hobart', 'SAE561', 'Hobart Salamander Grill with adjustable height heat source Electric Services: 4.0kW 400/50/3 Stainless Steel finish Variable height electric elements 2 Heating Zones Temperature control to each zone Chrome plated grid shelf Removable drip tray Dimensions: 600mm(w) x 510mm(d) x 510mm(h) Warranty: 1 Year Parts & Labour', 2001.73, 0.00, '1025-002', 'Oct 2025'),
      (c.id, 'HOB1-E0028', 'Hobart', 'SL350-10', 'The Hobart SL350-10 Gravity Feed Slicer is manufactured to the highest quality from anodised aluminum with a robust and reliable motor plus an integral sharpener ensuring your products are of the highest quality. Features: Detachable carriage & removable blade (tool supplied) makes cleaning easy. Precisely balanced for effortless slicing. Blade ring guard for safety when blade is removed. Interlocked carriage & gauge plate for safety. Built in two stone sharpener. Smooth, anodised aluminium body for hygiene. Indicator light for safety. Slices food up to 20mm thick. Fully CE marked. Dimensions: 575mm(w) x 615mm(d) x 530mm(h) Warranty: 1 Year Parts & Labour', 4143.00, 0.00, '0425-034', 'Apr 2025');
