      (c.id, 'MEI1-E0053-AC', 'Meiko', 'FB10M', 'FB10M Watercare FlowBoost10 rinse booster pump - designed for mains fed cold water to help increase the pressure up to a 1.5 bar increase over mains supply with WRAS approval. Flow rate up to 10 LPM with a 0.6 lmp activation. Maximum working pressure of 6 bar at 25°C. Full load current of 1.5 amps with continuous duty rating and an integrated check value. Working noise level typical 48dB with incorporated vibration damping feet, operating both thermal cut out and a dry run protection. Overall dimensions of cabinet will be 210mm wide x 383mm deep (including water connection on cabinet) x 340mm high.', 669.00, 0.00, '1225-062', 'Dec 2025'),
      (c.id, 'MEI1-E05005', 'Meiko', 'Warranty', 'Five (5) year no bills warranty offered on all front loading and pass-through ware washing machine(s) listed within our published pricelist that are provided with integral Meiko GiO reverse osmosis water treatment. Note:Annual planned preventative visits and six (6) monthly carbon filter exchange. In addition calls deemed as no fault found and operator misuse no salt in water softener machine contaminated with limescale etc. are also covered however we do reserve the right to request a meeting with customer to discuss such calls if they are deemed to be frequent and excessive in number. Carbon filter exchange to be undertaken by Customer. It needs to be clearly understood that failure to return the redundant filter cartridge to Meiko UK will result in the 3 year term No-bills guarantee bei', 2737.00, 0.00, '0426-030', 'Apr 2026'),
      (c.id, 'MEI1-E00032-AC', 'Meiko', '9750645-60', 'Four (4) x Round machine height extension legs to match the existing table working height of 890 mm.', 220.00, 0.00, '0425-071', 'Apr 2025'),
