      (c.id, 'SYN1-E0003', 'Synergy', 'ST1500', 'ST1500 Trilogy Grill with SMART control technology. Comes with garnish rail and slow cook shelf. 230v / 50Hz<1 kW via 13 amp socket. Dimensions: 1535mm(w) x 705mm(d) x 590mm(h) Warranty: 2 Years Parts and Labour', 8167.00, 0.00, '0125-045', 'Jan 2025'),
      (c.id, 'SYN1-E0009', 'Synergy', 'ST900E', 'Stainless steel construction, Two digital displays with touch control buttons, Temperature control up to 450°c, Fat is atomised, so no need for fat tray, Easy clean. Power Supply: 16 amp three phase, Electrical Power: Cord 2m power cord at the rear of the unit,Energy Consumption: 10kW, Elements: 2 cells containing 6 elements with SMART control, External Dimensions: WxDxH 905 x 835 x 590mm (with slow cook shelf and garnish rail), Area of Cooking Grid: 800 x 554mm (4432cm2) Warranty: 2 Year Parts and Labour.', 6264.00, 0.00, '1125-065', 'Nov 2025'),
      (c.id, 'SYN1-E00014', 'Synergy', 'CGO900E', 'Synergy CGO900E, stainless steel construction, operates as both an oven and grill, oven temperature control upto 250°c, two digital displays with touch button control. 1-10 grill power rating, fat atomised, no fat tray needed, easy clean. Power supply options: 5 pin 16 amp three phase, 5 pin 32 amp three phase, 400 Vac (L1=14 L2=14 L3=14). Electrical power cord: 2m power cord at the rear of the unit, energy comsumption: 10kW, Elements: 2 cells containing 6 elements with SMART control, Weight: 200kg including bars and garnish rails, surface cooking area: 800 x 554mm (4432cm2). Dimensions: 905mm(w) x 835mm(d) x 690mm(h) (705mm(d) without garnish rail) Depth with lid open: 890mm(d) (860mm without garnish rail) x 1160mm(h). Warranty: 2 Years Parts & Labour', 12870.00, 40.00, '0325-024', 'Mar 2025'),
      (c.id, 'SYN1-E0002', 'Synergy', 'ST600DI', 'Synergy Drop In ST600DI - Power Supply: 230v / 50Hz<1 kW via 13 amp socket, Electrical Power Cord: 1.5m with 3 pin plug at rear, Gas Natural or Propane Gas (inc Butane): convertible at site, Energy Consumption: Normal use = 5.7kW, Fast Heat Up for LPG and Natural Gas 6.8kW, Burners: One Burner with simple on/off switch - No thermocouples, Gas Connection: 3/4” BSP External Dimensions: 660mm(w) x 680mm(d) x 330mm(h) Area of Cooking Grid: 530 x 554mm (2936cm2) Warranty: 2 Years Parts & Labour', 3668.00, 0.00, '0925-012', 'Sep 2025'),
      (c.id, 'SYN1-E0004', 'Synergy', 'ST900DI', 'Synergy gas drop-in grill, 900mm wide', 8380.00, 40.00, '1025-048', 'Oct 2025'),
      (c.id, 'SYN1-E0025', 'Synergy', 'STCGO900DUAL', 'Synergy grill, operates as both an oven and grill, 2 digital displays with touch button controls, 2 variable heat zones, Fat atomised so no need for fat tray, 230v / 50Hz<1 kW 13 amp, 170kg Dimensions: 905mm (w) x 835mm (d) x 690mm (h) Warranty: 1 Year Parts & Labour Price includes mobile stand', 11176.00, 45.00, '1225-042', 'Dec 2025'),
      (c.id, 'SYN1-E00012', 'Synergy', 'ST900G', 'Synergy Trillogy Gas Grill ST900 with SMART Control, 800 x 754mm (6032cm2) cooking surface, Includes 200mm slow cook shelf, SMART controller with fast heat-up system, Natural Gas or LPG Gas, 11.4kw normal use (14kw during rapid heat up), 3/4" BSP gas connection. Unit comes with Garnish Rail and Slow Cook Shelf Dimensions: 905mm(w) x 835mm(d) x 590mm(h) Warranty: 2 Years Parts and Labour', 5417.40, 0.00, '0925-009', 'Sep 2025'),
      (c.id, 'SYN1-E00215', 'Synergy', 'ST1300 (Trilogy)', 'Synergy Trilogy 1300 Chargrill Variable natural gas indoor/outdoor model complete with 1200mm x 554mm grilling area (3) Adjustable power which is for each burners adjustable cast iron grid on/off switch stainless steel construction Elec: 230v/50/1-ph cord & plug Gas: 17.1 gas kW 64 489 BTU (field convertible to propane or butane). Supplied with: 1 No. Slow cook shelf and 1 No. Garnish Rail. Dimensions: 1304mm(w) x 705mm(d) x 530mm(h) Warranty: 2 Years Parts & Labour NOTE: Other accessories available to purchase at additional cost.', 7003.00, 0.00, '0325-085', 'Mar 2025'),
      (c.id, 'SYN1-E00180', 'Synergy', 'CGO900DUALE', 'Synergy Trilogy 900 Chargrill Variable electric indoor/outdoor model, Operates as both an oven and a chargrill complete with 800 x 554mm grilling area, 2 cells containing 6 elements with SMART control. Supplied with: Oven hood to 50% of cook area, 1 No. Slow cook shelf and 1No. Resting Shelf to 50% of cook area and, 1 No. Garnish Rail to full width Power: 10kW (16amp) three phase Dimensions: 905mm(w) x 835mm(d) x 690mm(h) (with garnish rail) (1005mm high with lid open) Warranty: 2 Year Parts & Labour', 12114.00, 40.00, '0325-024', 'Mar 2025'),
      (c.id, 'SYN1-E00115', 'Synergy', 'ST900', 'Synergy Trilogy 900 Chargrill Variable natural gas indoor/outdoor model complete with 800mm x 500mm grilling area (2) burners adjustable cast iron grid on/off switch stainless steel construction. Supplied with: 1 No. Slow cook shelf and 1 No. Garnish Rail. Power: 230v/50/1-ph cord & plug 11.4 gas kW 42 993 BTU (field convertible to propane or butane). Dimensions: 905mm(w) x 646mmmm(d) x 530mm(h) Warranty: 2 Years Parts & Labour Price includes for the following: A) Resting Shelf B) Mobile stand', 9029.00, 40.00, '0426-055', 'Apr 2026'),
      (c.id, 'SYN1-E00106', 'Synergy', 'ST900D', 'Synergy Trilogy ST900D', 4811.40, 0.00, '0425-025', 'Apr 2025'),
      (c.id, 'SYN1-E00015', 'Synergy', 'STCGO900', 'The Synergy Grill CharGo STCGO900 chargrill oven is an innovative highly efficient chargrill and oven combination, designed to significantly reduce cooking times and cost, without impact the quality, taste or texture of the food. Fitted with the new SMART control technology, this new controller places your grill onto a rapid heat up stage for 30 minutes to allow the grill to reach the cooking temperature faster, after which point it will automatically adjust to whatever your desired set temperature is. Tactile buttons allow you to control the unit in 1?C increments giving you full control over your cooking experience. The Synergy ST900 increases the scope of your menu even further (pizza, vegetables, bread, large joints of meat, ribs, whole chickens). You can even smoke food as this unit g', 7155.00, 0.00, '0325-105', 'Mar 2025'),
      (c.id, 'SYN1-E0600', 'Synergy Grill', 'ST600E', 'Synergy Chargrill electric model complete with 530 x 754mm grilling area, Stainless steel construction Digital display with touch button control with SMART control technology 1-10 grill power rating One variable heat zone Comes with Garnish Rail and Slow Cook Shelf Fat is atomised, so no need for fat tray Easy clean Power: 5 pin 16 amp three phase or 5 pin 32 amp three phase 400 Vac (L1=10 L2=10 L3=10), 2m power cord at the rear of unit, 6.7kW Energy Consumption. Dimensions: WxDxH 605 x 835 x 590mm (with slow cook shelf and garnish rail) Warranty: Two Year Parts and Labour.', 4458.00, 0.00, '1225-039', 'Dec 2025'),
      (c.id, 'SYN1-E00392', 'SynergyGrill', 'ST600', 'Gas Trilogy grill with One burner, with simple on/o_x001F_ switch SMART control technology with fast heat up system, NEW Digital display NEW Touch control buttons NEW 1 - 10 power rating NEW Control boards - Ease of programming for engineers NEW Pactrol software - Allowing for a stronger signal for flame detection Supply: 230v / 50Hz<1 kW via 13 amp socket Gas connection - 3/4" BSP Normal use = 5.7kW Fast Heat Up for LPG and Natural Gas 7kW Dimnesions: 605mm(w) x 835mm(d) x 590mm(h) (with slow cook shelf and garnish rail) Warranty: 1Year Parts & Labour ** Unit comes with garnish rail and slow cook shelf ** Price includes mobile stand', 6706.00, 45.00, '1225-042', 'Dec 2025'),
      (c.id, 'TCS1-E0002', 'TCS Chandlery Ltd', 'Plastimo 8-3010', 'Plastimo 20Ltr jerrycan water container with pouring spout. Manufactured from food quality polyethylene suitable for drinking water. Size: H455mm x L350mm x W165mm Capacity: 20Ltr', 21.99, 0.00, '0525-055', 'May 2025'),
      (c.id, 'TEF1-E0006', 'Tefcold', 'DB201H', 'Back Bar Cooler, fully automatic, fan assisted cooling, +2 to +10°C temperature range, digital controller and temperature display with protective cover, automatic defrost type, (2) hinged glass doors, double glazed tempered glass, lock, black exterior finish, stucco aluminium interior finish, (4) adjustable shelves, adjustable feet, LED interior light, R600a refrigerant, Climate Class: 4, Energy Rating: A, Energy Consumption: 394kWh per Annum, 13 amps Dimensions:900mm (w) x 520mm (d) x 870mm (h) Warranty: 2 Years Parts & 1 Year Labour', 451.00, 0.00, '0426-069', 'Apr 2026'),
      (c.id, 'ELD1-E00012', 'Tefcold', 'EL22SS (ECO DESIGN)', 'Chest Freezer, solid lid with lock, digital temperature display, static cooling, -23°C to -16°C temperature range, interior light, mains indicator light, white interior and exterior finish, (1) basket, with feet, defrost drain, R600a refrigerant, Climate Class: 3, Energy Rating: C, Energy Consumption: 344kWh per Annum, 13 amps. Dimensions: 720mm(w) x 739mm(d) x 861mm(h) Warranty:1 Year Parts & Labour', 823.00, 35.00, '0325-042', 'Mar 2025'),
      (c.id, 'TEF1-E0008', 'Tefcold', 'BC85', 'Tefcold Undercounter Chiller, fully automatic, fan assisted, lock, adjustable shelves, adjustable feet, interior led light with switch, digital temperature display, curved profile door, R600a, 13 amp Dimensions: 503mm(w) x 567mm(d) x 775mm(h) Warranty: 2 Years Parts & 1 Year Labour', 295.00, 0.00, '0525-006', 'May 2025'),
      (c.id, 'INT1-E02947', 'Tefcold', 'ST160', 'Tefcold® Chest Freezer, 550mm W, 115 litre/4.1 cu. ft. capacity, (1) basket, -14° to -24°C adjustable temperature range, defrost drain, flat hinged glass lid, lock fitted, white interior & exterior, fully automatic operation, manual defrost with drain, fitted castors (except on ST160 packed inside), R600a, MEPS D Dimensions: 550mm(w) x 550mm(d) x 870mm(h) Warranty: Two Year Parts & One year Labour', 440.99, 0.00, '0725-006', 'Jul 2025'),
      (c.id, 'TEF1-E00010', 'Tefcold', 'GM200SS', 'Tefcold® Chest Freezer, 734mm W, 185-litre/6.53 cu.ft. interior capacity, -14° to -24°C adjustable temperature range, mains indicator light, includes (2) baskets, static cooling, manual defrost with drain, stainless steel lid with lock, white interior & exterior, self-contained refrigeration, castors, R600a, 150 watts, MEPS F. Dimensions: 734mm(w) x 680mm(d) x 920mm(h) Warranty: 2 Years Parts Only', 340.00, 0.00, '1125-043', 'Nov 2025'),
      (c.id, 'TEF1-E00011', 'Tefcold', 'RK500', 'Tefcold® Refrigerator, one-section, 680mm W, 450 litre/15.9 cu. ft. capacity, (3) adjustable shelves, lock fitted solid door with replaceable door gaskets, -2° to +8°C adjustable temperature range, digital display/controller, automatic defrost, bottom mounted self contained refrigeration, stainless steel exterior & interior, R600a, 353 watts, MEPS C. Dimensions: 680mm(w) x 700mm(d) x 1900mm(h) Warranty: 2 Years Parts & 1 Year Labour', 779.35, 0.00, '0126-077', 'Jan 2026'),
      (c.id, 'TEL1-E0002', 'Telcold', 'TFW400-2S', 'Wine Cooler, Stainless steel door frame and handle, 2 temperature zones with a max. of 10°C variation, Energy efficient cooling system, Low noise level, LED interior light with switch, Reversible glass door, Wooden shelves, High/low temperature alarm, Presentation shelves available as option, black exterior finish,Interior Finish: Black ABS, Net Weight: 106kg", automatic defrost type, R600a refrigerant, Climate Class: 4Energy Rating: G,Energy Consumption: 175kWh per Annum, 13 amps Dimensions: 595mm(w) x 680mm(d) x 760mm(h) Warranty: 2 Years Parts & 1 Year Labour', 908.70, 0.00, '0825-039', 'Aug 2025');
