      (c.id, 'TFSE1-E00002', 'TFSE', 'BESPOKE', '"Bespoke Three Door Fridge 1900w x 815d x 540h. Stainless steel construction with hinged Stainless Steel doors, Concealed Hinges with spring closing. External Satin burnished, Internal Polished,. Ventilated cooling 4- 8°C with adjustable shelves (two per section) Integral Compressor configured with front venting Power 230v 13a" Warranty: 1 Year Parts & Labour', 3810.00, 0.00, '0925-068', 'Sep 2025'),
      (c.id, 'TFS1-E0007', 'TFSE', 'Aged', 'Ages Brass Pattina', 670.00, 0.00, '0426-001', 'Apr 2026'),
      (c.id, 'TFSE1-E00006', 'TFSE', 'DCP1800-BSP', 'Bespoke Upright Ambient Display cabinet. construction is in sections for site assembly. Construction: welded, polished stainless panelling and framing. Lower part cabinet with stainless steel two-door lockable section across approx 1200w x 800h. Above, a double-door hinged glass cabinet with polished Stainless Steel hinges and handles. Right section of cabinet with full-height hinged glass door. Behind the glass door section, adjustable glass shelving. All glass is toughened. Mirror to the rear wall to enhance visuals. LED24v warm white all around the door, Perimeter, and panel sides. The rear and Right panels are solid construction. Left cabinet, side-glazed above 800 height. Dimensions: 1800mm(w) x 700mm(d) x 2650mm(h) Warranty: 12 months (2 years Compressor)', 5725.00, 0.00, '1225-051', 'Dec 2025'),
      (c.id, 'TFS1-E0005', 'TFSE', 'MF1000-BSP', 'Bespoke ventilated refrigerated display cabinet for meat ageing, featuring hanging rails and adjustable shelving. The external cabinet with polished brass trims and double-glazed front glass and rear hinged doors, Sides are clad in insulated stainless steel panels, with a Himalayan salt block, illuminated from the rear. Internal LED lighting, warm white at 2700 - 3000 K, is fitted on the ceiling and along the front corners. The construction is of stainless steel, with a top-mounted evaporator and EC compact blower fans. The compressor is to be located within 5 metres of the upper wall section of the Prep Kitchen. Remote Control Panel for temperature settings of 2 - 8 °c and controlled humidity for meat ageing, alongside UV disinfection. Power supply is 230V. 13a.Freon R290a. Dimensions: 10', 8245.00, 0.00, '0525-107', 'May 2025'),
      (c.id, 'TFS1-E0006', 'TFSE', 'Locks', 'Locks', 110.00, 0.00, '0426-001', 'Apr 2026'),
      (c.id, 'TFS1-E0003', 'TFSE', 'Chaffing dish', 'TFSE chaffing dish', 700.00, 0.00, '0325-012', 'Mar 2025'),
      (c.id, 'TFS1-E0004', 'TFSE', 'Heated Lowerator', 'TFSE Heated Lowerator', 750.00, 0.00, '0325-012', 'Mar 2025'),
      (c.id, 'TFS1-E0002', 'TFSE', 'Induction', 'TFSE Induction system', 18770.00, 0.00, '0325-012', 'Mar 2025'),
      (c.id, 'TFS1-E0009', 'TFSE Products Ltd', 'UC2085-3DR-4', 'Bespoke Under Counter top fridge 2085w x 650d x 710h.Stainless steel 304 grade construction with four set x 3 1/1 Gastronorm sliding Drawers approx. 120mm height. Drawer with Replaceable Gaskets, ventilated cooling 2/6C with integral compressor with compressor venting in and out user side. Self evaporation defrost condensate. Low level adjustable feet. Power 230v 13a R290 Warranty: 1 Year Parts and Labour', 5770.00, 0.00, '0725-001', 'Jul 2025'),
      (c.id, 'TFS1-E00010', 'TFSE Products Ltd', 'UC1630-3DR-3', 'Bespoke under-counter top fridge 1630w x 650d x 710h.Stainless steel 304 grade construction with three x three sets (non-Gastronorm) sliding Drawers, approx. 180mm height. Drawer with Replaceable Gaskets, ventilated cooling 2/6C with integral compressor with compressor venting in and out user side. Self-evaporation defrost condensate. Low-level adjustable feet. Power 230v 13a R290 Warranty: 1 Year Parts and Labour', 3825.00, 0.00, '0725-001', 'Jul 2025'),
      (c.id, 'TFS1-E06000', 'TFSE Products Ltd', 'Bespoke', 'Bespoke ventilated refrigerated display cabinet for fish ageing, featuring hanging rails and adjustable shelving. Overall dimensions are 850mm (w) x 550mm (d) x 1400mm (h). The external cabinet with polished brass trims and double-glazed front glass hinged doors, Sides are clad in insulated stainless steel panels with wood layered by the client. Internal rear wall Himalayan salt block, illuminated from the rear. Internal LED lighting, warm white at 2700 - 3000 K, fitted on the ceiling and along the front corners. Construction 316 stainless steel, with a top-mounted Condensing unit. Temperature settings of 0 - 8 °c and controlled humidity for meat ageing, alongside UV disinfection. Power supply is 230V. 13a.Freon R290a. Price includes for door locks and aged Brass Patina. Warranty: 12 Month', 8440.00, 0.00, '0426-001', 'Apr 2026'),
      (c.id, 'TFS1-E05500-INS', 'TFSE Products Ltd', 'Delvery & Install', 'Delivery & Install', 1200.00, 0.00, '0725-083', 'Jul 2025'),
